{"tid":1950034,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香里奈曾是木村山P劇集女一　洩開腿床照衰6年","createTime":"2020-03-30T05:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T09:24:45.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c0885420e495a347d3c4dd9b7ca6a23dcc4fce3f","tid":1950034,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"近日最受歡迎的日劇，必屬《戀愛可以持續到天長地久》，由佐藤健演出毒舌又帥氣的天堂醫生，令女粉絲紛紛出現心心眼。不過在劇中飾演天堂醫生胞姊流子的香里奈，卻是顏值大幅崩壞，現年36歲的她，外觀是40歲大媽，本來的清純玉女，因為2014年的淫照事件，事業毀於一旦，相當可惜。"},{"pid":"4c60cf1f84ca9a3e4ae4cf1251183c15fb056e47","tid":1950034,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4234381/org/9669218179db147bde38f99cc5dd7089.jpg/mID8UXI9lrBHxaVUoAgVqzWnJDjxt9anesesdHrHrHQ?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4234381%2Forg%2F9669218179db147bde38f99cc5dd7089.jpg%2FmID8UXI9lrBHxaVUoAgVqzWnJDjxt9anesesdHrHrHQ%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=27e497c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香里奈顏值和身材也是頂級女星，可惜因為床照而毀盡星途。"},{"pid":"39e59c7dc881b7c7e3365b76525a4ef18eb28e45","tid":1950034,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:20:26.000Z","msg":"當一班女劇迷被佐藤健電倒的時候，其實劇中還有一位女星，令人萬分震驚，她就是劇中佐藤健的胞姊，現年36歲的香里奈，角色癲喪又喜愛飲酒，是一個情緒大起大落的人物，雖然喜感十足，但她的真實星途卻是相當可惜，在千禧年香里奈是日本時尚雜誌《Ray》首席專屬模特兒，顏值爆燈，有著一雙會笑的眼睛，身材亦無可挑剔，先後在木村拓哉主演的《Priceless無價人生》(2012)，飾演女主角二階堂彩矢，《SUMMER NUDE》(2013)飾演千代原夏希，跟型男山下智久成為一對，正受力捧上位的她，卻因為一宗淫照醜聞，前程盡毀。"},{"pid":"00b983769acb49adc0f833f215c4f8b36a8c7d6f","tid":1950034,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4234409/org/78454973b97a874302aa8e38678fa34a.jpg/XGWgmQLyMDyJ7lQ_i9LvQ9LOB9ABwh5IuftUp7n7VKc?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4234409%2Forg%2F78454973b97a874302aa8e38678fa34a.jpg%2FXGWgmQLyMDyJ7lQ_i9LvQ9LOB9ABwh5IuftUp7n7VKc%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c96e5902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4234404/org/04543c3a8f4abc55f4383ea013b72646.jpg/MjfNN--vnPTdNOrBpuV7iEgx9-D06N_D3diddt3YnXY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4234404%2Forg%2F04543c3a8f4abc55f4383ea013b72646.jpg%2FMjfNN--vnPTdNOrBpuV7iEgx9-D06N_D3diddt3YnXY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0ac8918b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4234391/org/2db84fb42ef631073b4a50457d15c4e7.jpg/nuoLD3XMOJCKCBstQl3iMebSsmcU6y4DlNWC5pTVguY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4234391%2Forg%2F2db84fb42ef631073b4a50457d15c4e7.jpg%2FnuoLD3XMOJCKCBstQl3iMebSsmcU6y4DlNWC5pTVguY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=14d90963&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d997655b498bd6cb88eb4e37daf148038bffb85","tid":1950034,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:21:21.000Z","msg":"在2014年日本雜誌《FRIDAY》，刊登了一張香里奈的床照，相中的她雙腿張開，以右手遮著下體，報導指香里奈當時跟一名台灣富二代拍拖，而為了學好英文，她曾到夏威夷短期留學，適逢有同學生日，她們遂包下酒店套房開生日派對，而香里奈酒醉後，跟男友在房間發生關係，之後倦極而睡，其中一位朋友將她的性感睡姿拍下，最後照片被雜誌曝光。香里奈一向的玉女形象，因淫照事件而嚴重受損，被《Ray》雜誌叮走外，之後的電視劇亦淪為大配角，加上隨著歲月而變得蒼老，昔日的甜姐兒外貌，再不復見，令人痛心。"},{"pid":"278674ec2fe602203c7568339bad2a0761e733be","tid":1950034,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4234415/org/5a3cb7cfe998752ee0896be6479d4a7f.jpg/sOTlHtez1O2plbzRkYRfZyavrq4NhLXo-iD5Y_og-WM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4234415%2Forg%2F5a3cb7cfe998752ee0896be6479d4a7f.jpg%2FsOTlHtez1O2plbzRkYRfZyavrq4NhLXo-iD5Y_og-WM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ee8823ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4234413/org/ffb3214b0d636c297d8c541233771e2a.jpg/bRyFx2SGNfVikHqhwYw_aVKIY0Gjl_enl2_9VJdv_VQ?v=w1280\" data-thumb